Package administration.daos

Class AbstractUserEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • administration.daos.AbstractUserEntity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    User

    @Entity
public abstract class AbstractUserEntity
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Max. This class represents the abstract database entry for a user. It contains an id, a version, a creation date, an update date and the last login date of the user.
